parameters: It's locked though.\! You don't know his locker combination by any chance, do you?
I don't.\! \BST[1]But look at that note on his locker.
Oh ya, something's written.\! Let's see...
Knowing him, this is probably a clue to figuring out his locker combination.
Those colors...\! I feel like there's a pattern to them somehow.
Let's try this for his locker combination...
Tap the screen with two fingers or right-click to backspace!
It's a letter.\! Here, can I read it?
My fieldtrip itinerary was approved so no one will suspect a thing.\! And I've got our special room already reserved.\! Don't forget to
tell your Sister that you'll be gone a few days for a 'study program'.
We're staying in a private deluxe suite in The Underground.\! I'm bringing some new
sexy outfits just for you baby ♥️♥️♥️

He's been getting freaky with Mrs. Johnson!
But think about what that might mean Nadia!
The letter said she booked a room in The Underground.
I don't think it's really a place you should go visit, however...
But I do know that the people in that district didn't turn into zombies.
If that's where they are then...
The letter said she booked a room in some place called The Underground.
But for all we know, that part of the city could be safer.
Outside of our district, the rest of the city might not have zombies.
If they weren't in the school that day then...
Uh-oh.\! You're not upset at her, are you?
No...\! \BST[6]I'm just so relieved to know he's alright.
*sniffle*\! I didn't want to admit it, but I was beginning to lose hope.
I thought that...\! that maybe he had turned into one of those monsters...
I have a feeling you're right Nadia.
But I also have a feeling we won't be if we stay around here any longer...
I'm all for supporting the school team but I'm not a fan of athletic zombies...
I don't think that was the right combination...
Those colors...\! I feel like there's a pattern to them somehow.
Have you seen anything in the school that's matched those colors?
Some of the lockers in the school are out of place.\! \BST[1]Maybe those are related?
